      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolute pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for something that's been loved and kept in perfect shape, this is definitely the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
