    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a pristine example of the ultimate driving machine, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. The engine utilizes individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing for razor-sharp throttle response across the entire power band. Mechanically, this vehicle is impeccable: the rod bearings have been addressed, and the rear subframe has been reinforced to ensure structural integrity under high torque loads. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential that offers superb lateral grip. Every component, from the cooling system to the suspension bushings, reflects a rigorous maintenance schedule aimed at preserving original performance specs. This is a collector-grade chassis with zero mechanical compromises.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
