    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example that redefines what it means to be 'showroom quality.' This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, protected from the elements since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips or swirl marks, further enhanced by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any creasing or wear, and it still retains that distinct new-car aroma. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It comes with a comprehensive, binder-organized service history, including a recent major inspection and fluid flush performed by master technicians. Every feature, from the advanced infotainment system to the heated seats, functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. This is a collector-grade vehicle for the discerning buyer who refuses to compromise on quality.",
